movie.title: Gifted Hands: The Ben Carson Story
movie.plot: Biography of Ben Carson who grew up to be Dr. Ben Carson, a world famous neurosurgeon at Johns Hopkins.
movie.awards: Nominated for 4 Primetime Emmys. Another 8 wins & 11 nominations.
